Install from binary
-------------------

To install from binary, mount the disk image and drag and drop the
XNJB package. Then double click on XNJB to run.

Install from source
-------------------

Untar the source with something like this:

tar -xjvf xnjb-0.11.tar.bz2

and double click on XNJB.xcode. If you don't have XCode installed
please install it from the Developer CD or download for free from
developer.apple.com.

Compile by clicking Build from the Build menu. You can choose a
development or deployment build from the Styles tab in Get Info on
the XNJB project. Then run XNJB from the build directory.

